370
00:38:08,140 --> 00:38:10,390
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku pulang.</font>

371
00:38:10,390 --> 00:38:12,340
<font color=#FFFF00>Kenapa kau minum banyak sekali?</font>

372
00:38:12,340 --> 00:38:18,160
