373
00:38:18,160 --> 00:38:22,460
<font color=#FFFF00>Maaf. Aku cuma minum sedikit bir.</font>

374
00:38:22,460 --> 00:38:24,930
<font color=#FFFF00>Kenapa jadi ada banyak pertemuan?</font>

375
00:38:24,930 --> 00:38:27,010
<font color=#FFFF00>Tunggu, aku yakin ada obat di sekitar sini--</font>

376
00:38:27,010 --> 00:38:29,960
<font color=#FFFF00>Jangan pergi, tetap di sini.</font>

377
00:38:29,960 --> 00:38:34,150
<font color=#FFFF00>Ah, bau alkohol.
