381
00:38:46,130 --> 00:38:48,340
<font color=#FFFF00>Maaf sudah bohong.</font>

382
00:38:55,480 --> 00:38:57,360
<font color=#FFFF00>Maafkan aku.</font>

383
00:39:37,490 --> 00:39:40,960
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku harus membencimu sampai mati.</font>

384
00:39:43,660 --> 00:39:46,690
<font color=#FFFF00>Kenapa aku sangat merindukanmu?</font>

385
00:40:04,690 --> 00:40:08,100
<font color=#FFFF00>Hey, Joon Seo.</font>

386
00:40:08,100 --> 00:40:12,840
<font color=#FFFF00>Orang tua kita masih sama.</font>

387
00:40:18,650 --> 00:40:24,240
<font color=#FFFF00>Selama sebulan penuh, mereka hanya memasak <i>kkotgetang.</i></font>

388
00:40:24,240 --> 00:40:31,550
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa ada orang lain yang bisa aku curhati selain darimu?</font>

389
00:40:31,550 --> 00:40:35,500
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau satu-satunya yang kupercaya di dunia ini, Joon Seo.</font>

390
00:40:35,500 --> 00:40:37,110
<font color=#FFFF00>Hyeong.</font>

391
00:40:38,250 --> 00:40:39,950
<font color=#FFFF00>Hyeong.</font>

392
00:40:39,950 --> 00:40:43,730
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa?</font>

393
00:40:43,730 --> 00:40:47,930
