394
00:40:47,930 --> 00:40:49,000
<font color=#FFFF00>Di mana dia?</font>

395
00:40:52,120 --> 00:40:54,130
<font color=#FFFF00>Jo Taek Sang.</font>

396
00:40:55,690 --> 00:40:57,620
<font color=#FFFF00>H-Halo.</font>

397
00:40:57,620 --> 00:40:59,790
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau ingat aku?</font>

398
00:40:59,790 --> 00:41:06,740
<font color=#FFFF00>Tentu. Aku sangat menyesal.
