404
00:41:26,380 --> 00:41:27,870
<font color=#FFFF00>Lalu kenapa...</font>

405
00:41:27,870 --> 00:41:31,490
<font color=#FFFF00>Hei, yang di sana.
Ya, kau.</font>

406
00:41:33,500 --> 00:41:35,390
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa kau Jo Taek Sang?</font>

407
00:41:35,390 --> 00:41:37,220
<font color=#FFFF00>Ya.</font>

408
00:41:37,220 --> 00:41:39,310
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau kenal aku, kan?</font>

409
00:41:43,060 --> 00:41:44,800
<font color=#FFFF00>Hei, brengsek!</font>

410
00:42:19,610 --> 00:42:20,610
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau tak apa?</font>

411
00:42:20,610 --> 00:42:23,320
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku baik.</font>

412
00:42:54,420 --> 00:42:57,920
<font color=#FFFF00>Jangan kemari, brengsek!</font>

413
00:43:15,730 --> 00:43:17,540
<font color=#FFFF00>Cepat pergi!</font>

414
00:44:01,960 --> 00:44:06,770
<font color=#FFFF00>Kenapa kau datang dari Bukcheon
ke Seoul demi Jo Taek Sang?</font>

415
00:44:06,770 --> 00:44:09,440
<font color=#FFFF00>Orang itu bukan Jo Taek Sang.</font>

416
00:44:09,440 --> 00:44:13,870
<font color=#FFFF00>Dia yang kami kejar sebelumnya
