422
00:44:33,010 --> 00:44:35,860
<font color=#FFFF00>Siapa pemilik mobilnya?</font>

423
00:44:35,860 --> 00:44:39,890
<font color=#FFFF00>Jeong Hye. Yoon Jeong Hye.</font>

424
00:44:49,090 --> 00:44:50,790
<font color=#FFFF00>Mungkin ini...</font>

425
00:44:53,080 --> 00:44:56,110
<font color=#FFFF00>Ya, ini dia.</font>

426
00:45:00,560 --> 00:45:05,280
<font color=#FFFF00>Bisa kau beritahu sedikit padaku tentang Yoon Jeong Hye?</font>

427
00:45:05,280 --> 00:45:07,580
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau juga kenal dia?</font>

428
00:45:07,580 --> 00:45:09,050
<font color=#FFFF00>Iya.</font>

429
00:45:09,050 --> 00:45:12,970
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau kenal baik? Mungkin, kau
memeriksa latar belakangnya</font>

430
00:45:12,970 --> 00:45:16,180
<font color=#FFFF00>Hanya namanya.
Aku cuma tahu namanya.</font>

431
00:45:17,790 --> 00:45:23,100
<font color=#FFFF00>Yah, aku tak bisa bilang rinciannya
