432
00:45:23,100 --> 00:45:25,710
<font color=#FFFF00>Tolong beritahu aku.</font>

433
00:45:27,030 --> 00:45:28,920
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau siapa?</font>

434
00:45:28,920 --> 00:45:31,080
<font color=#FFFF00>Tolong beritahu aku.</font>

435
00:45:31,080 --> 00:45:36,350
<font color=#FFFF00>Wanita macam apa Yoon Jeong Hye?
