443
00:46:20,060 --> 00:46:23,870
<font color=#FFFF00>Ya. Hubungi aku jika ada apa-apa.</font>

444
00:46:23,870 --> 00:46:25,970
<font color=#FFFF00>Baik.</font>

445
00:46:30,720 --> 00:46:32,330
<font color=#FFFF00>Siapa?</font>

446
00:46:32,330 --> 00:46:34,950
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau kenal Yoon Jeong Hye, kan?</font>

447
00:46:34,950 --> 00:46:39,080
<font color=#FFFF00>Yoon Jeong Hye?</font>

448
00:46:39,080 --> 00:46:41,390
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau dekat dengannya?</font>

449
00:46:41,390 --> 00:46:43,050
<font color=#FFFF00>Ya, tapi kau siapa?</font>

450
00:46:43,050 --> 00:46:47,120
<font color=#FFFF00>Saya Ketua Tim Jang Joon Seo dari
