458
00:47:08,920 --> 00:47:11,390
<font color=#FFFF00>Kapan terakhir kau bertemu Yoon Jeong Hye?</font>

459
00:47:11,390 --> 00:47:15,930
<font color=#FFFF00>Kami agak dekat saat kuliah tapi sekarang
