464
00:47:34,130 --> 00:47:35,970
<font color=#FFFF00>Siapa dia...</font>

465
00:47:35,970 --> 00:47:39,790
<font color=#FFFF00>Siapa bajingan ini...</font>

466
00:47:39,790 --> 00:47:42,370
<font color=#FFFF00>Kenapa dia begini...
<i>Yoon Jeong Hye</i></font>

467
00:47:42,370 --> 00:47:45,550
<font color=#FFFF00>Ini.</font>

468
00:47:49,020 --> 00:47:51,590
<font color=#FFFF00>Maaf ya! Itu mejaku.</font>

469
00:47:51,590 --> 00:47:54,210
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Saat piknik dengan teman-temanku.</i></font>

470
00:48:09,470 --> 00:48:13,570
<font color=#FFFF00>Permisi. Halo. Ini ruanganku.</font>

471
00:48:13,570 --> 00:48:15,450
<font color=#FFFF00>Dan ini komputerku.</font>

472
00:48:15,450 --> 00:48:17,400
<font color=#FFFF00>Menurut hukum, ini masalah---</font>

473
00:48:17,400 --> 00:48:21,580
<font color=#FFFF00>Orang kurang ajar macam apa yang
