491
00:50:27,060 --> 00:50:32,450
<font color=#FFFF00>Ibu, apa pendapatmu soal keluarga Jang?</font>

492
00:50:32,450 --> 00:50:35,180
<font color=#FFFF00>Kenapa tiba-tiba kau bahas keluarga itu?</font>

493
00:50:35,180 --> 00:50:36,990
