517
00:52:10,850 --> 00:52:12,580
<font color=#FFFF00>Dong Seok Hyeong.</font>

518
00:52:13,640 --> 00:52:14,540
<font color=#FFFF00>Joon Seo.</font>

519
00:52:14,540 --> 00:52:17,200
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau bilang akan menelepon.</font>

520
00:52:17,200 --> 00:52:19,780
<font color=#FFFF00>Ada beberapa sidang di pagi hari
