522
00:52:25,170 --> 00:52:28,460
<font color=#FFFF00>Hey, jika jaksa sibuk, aku juga.</font>

523
00:52:28,460 --> 00:52:33,420
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku detektif, alasan itu hanya
